body:
Download the source code, extract, and run [CMake](https://cmake.org). 

Or, download the respective binary package for your platform, which includes engine binaries.

For compiling instructions, please check our [Windows](http://wiki.torque3d.org/coder:compiling-in-windows) and [Linux](http://wiki.torque3d.org/coder:compiling-in-linux) pages.

Download the source code, extract, and run [Project Manager](https://github.com/GarageGames/Torque3D-ProjectManager/releases/download/v2.2/Project-Manager-v2.2.zip) or CMake.

name: 3.7 release candidate
body: Download `Torque3D-3.7rc-Win.zip`, extract, and run `Project Manager.exe`. Binaries are only available for Windows in this pre-release; to compile in Linux, see [these instructions](http://wiki.torque3d.org/coder:compiling-in-linux).
